
Overview of noun calumny

The noun calumny has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (1) defamation, calumny, calumniation, obloquy, traducement, hatchet job -- (a false accusation of an offense or a malicious misrepresentation of someone's words or actions)
2. aspersion, calumny, slander, defamation, denigration -- (an abusive attack on a person's character or good name)
